## Conventions

- Note anything here that would otherwise surprise a future session: a
  self-signed cert that needs `curl -sk`, a probe that needs a short
  timeout, a naming convention for scripts that talk to a device.
- **Memory is keyed to the exact directory you launch your agent from** —
  always launch from this workspace root, or memory silently won't load.
  This is the one gotcha worth a permanent line here.
